title: Alphabet shares surge as Google profit beats street
text:
Alphabet shares surge as Google profit beats street 
The Star Friday 23rd October, 2015 
Different revenue streams: Video advertising on YouTube got the credit for helping Alphabet gain a 45% jump in profit, along with money from advertising in search results on mobile devices. -- Reuters
